{"tid":553120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（無圖）啱啱坐地鐵大陸細佬比人串","createTime":"2018-02-07T07:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T08:25:17.000Z","uid":65207,"like":28,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"749f72fadb05290e116795a787d2518dff5e808a","tid":553120,"uid":65207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T07:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/135049_45f5ef94bac4ec424c74e8b01c10adaa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F135049_45f5ef94bac4ec424c74e8b01c10adaa.png&h=aba44a29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啱啱坐地鐵 理站就有個大陸細佬衝過泥想搶關愛坐<br />\n不過比個伯伯坐左先  <br />\n個細佬阿媽就用普通話講 都話你上車見到就要衝過去加啦 你睇下搶唔到無位坐喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細佬重話我今次因爲跑得唔夠快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個伯伯一聽到（紅圈個個）用返普通話講 你地呢啲大陸人個個都係識搶咩都都搶老人家都唔放過 不過我知你唔同既 你讓左個位比我<br />\n個阿媽就係到講唔好噪喇 全車人睇住佢柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好笑係伯伯係到串鳩個細佬佢重唔知柒咁係到答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他人笑到get get聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf12d78a7a114eafc83010b4deded55d13cbc50d","tid":553120,"uid":65207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51877c3117e49aea2818be893a589ecca9f0cac1","tid":553120,"uid":65207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T07:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920e7ccbbb5c85fa518dc829948995233f44c215","tid":553120,"uid":65207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T07:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8c